Eclipse IDE

Install Eclipse Plugins:
Checkstyle - http://eclipse-cs.sf.net/update/
FindBugs - http://findbugs.cs.umd.edu/eclipse/  
PMD - http://pmd.sourceforge.net/eclipse/
Maven integration - http://download.eclipse.org/technology/m2e/releases/

After instalation:

1. Activate plugins: 
Project->Properties->Checkstyle->Checkstyle active for this project
...same for PMD and findbugs.

2. Set common templates:
Project->Properties->Java Code Style->Clean Up->import src/main/config/build-tools/formatter/java-clean.xml
Project->Properties->Java Code Style->Code Templates->import src/main/config/build-tools/formatter/java-code-template.xml
Project->Properties->Java Code Style->Formatter->import src/main/config/build-tools/formatter/java-format.xml
